+# Rigging
+
+Project tooling values for Shipshape roles. Values only, not procedure.
+Procedure lives in the skills. Every role reads this on open.
+
+## Stack
+
+- language: JavaScript
+- runtime: node
+- packageManager: npm
+
+## Directories
+
+- implementation: src
+- specs: features
+- verification: features/support
+- assets: data
+- scantlings: none
+
+## Commands
+
+- discover: `npx cucumber-js --dry-run`
+- focused: `npx cucumber-js --name "{scenario}"`
+- broad: `npx cucumber-js --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- coverage: `npx c8 --include="src/**" --include="features/support/**" npx cucumber-js --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- step-usage: `npx cucumber-js --format usage-json --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- plank-inventory: `npx jsdoc -X src/**/*.js features/support/**/*.js`
+- typecheck: none
+- lint: `npx @biomejs/biome lint src/ features/`
+- conformance: none
+
+## Perturbation
+
+- message: `PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed`
+- perturb: `throw new Error("PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed");`
+
+## Tiers
+
+- default: @logic
+- sandbox: none
+- policy: default
+- weather: none
+- runrecord: logs/runrecord.json
+
+## Dependencies
+
+- policy: locked
+- dependency: @cucumber/cucumber@13.2.0
+
+## Outbound
+
+- outbound: none
+- ship: none
+- verify: none
\ No newline at end of file
